      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-4 mb-6">How to Convert Your Microsoft Power Apps Build Into a Native Mobile App</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">Want to unlock wider distribution and more flexibility for your Microsoft PowerApps project? MobiLoud will help you turn it into a native app that works great, feels fully native, and requires no extra work to maintain.</p>
